{"tid":1724983,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"14歲女與16歲男友偷嘗禁果　醫院職員揭發報警","createTime":"2019-11-15T15:23:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T17:12:42.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f400c9e43935a3f915351d179109c787afefcd5f","tid":1724983,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T15:23:57.000Z","msg":"油麻地小情侶偷嘗禁果，男友被捕。今午(15日)2時50分，警方接獲加士居道一間醫院職員報案，指懷疑一名14歲女童與其16歲男友曾發生性行為。警員到場調查，將案件列作「與年齡在十六歲以下的女童非法性交」，並拘捕涉案少年，案件交由油尖警區刑事調查隊跟進。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191115/bkn-20191115193627017-1115_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20191115%2Fbkn-20191115193627017-1115_00822_001.html&d=NKgE6Majit0rEYuBm%2F0CvmzUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=509d955e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191115/bkn-20191115193627017-1115_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"ec22d2ecaa62531f2b794d1d96eb434c4fa3d9b6","tid":1724983,"uid":190793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T15:25:42.000Z","msg":"借個位<br />\n韓國戰線要人呀！！完全冇人簽<br />\n［韓國戰線］青瓦台請願聯署 同我簽爆佢 （教學）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1720736\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1720736</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2599eaa3fffdfbd8c224eeac86ee1d5167537ffe","tid":1724983,"uid":134006,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T15:25:43.000Z","msg":"閪毛都未撚生齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e70fb61a3929744183ebae48e07d838bdc1b0bf5","tid":1724983,"uid":45613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T15:26:15.000Z","msg":"Fake"},{"pid":"658ed0967e5131eda856cfe4172b59fad38af2f4","tid":1724983,"uid":219010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T15:39:47.000Z","msg":"比人當天使?"},{"pid":"c96b79dae446be0b5c70bd74e2ad4e760a122fd0","tid